  "detailed_description": "<strong>Hope For Village</strong> is an Old-School RPG game. We designed this game for mini rpg & survival fans. Farming, crafting, combat, fishing and more, just explore it! <br>Monsters, wild animals, enemies of kingdom... Who do you think will win?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mini RPG Survival game!<br></li><li>You can loot items!<br></li><li>Craft new weapons!<br></li><li>Manage the basic farm system!<br></li><li>Buy new weapons and armors!<br></li><li>Fight with enemies and monsters!<br></li><li>You can fish!<br></li><li>You can cook!<br></li><li>You can be a miner!<br></li><li>Turn Based Combat System!<br></li><li>Sail your own boat!<br></li><li>Day & Night System!</li></ul><br>Explore the forest, discover secret places...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1005630/extras/3da68f67c641478ab67ab782c8cc91ec.avif?t=1575300436\" width=237 height=133 /></span>",
